'''彩色纸屑'''（{{lang-it|Coriandoli}}），指以聚脂薄膜或[[金属材料|金属材料]]为原料的多种色彩的纸片碎屑，通常用于[[巡遊|巡遊]]，[[运动会|运动会]]等庆祝活动，特别是婚礼庆祝上。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.yourdictionary.com/confetti |title=American Heritage Dictionary |publisher=Yourdictionary.com |date=2014-06-20 |accessdate=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2016-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107231600/http://www.yourdictionary.com/confetti }}</ref>早期的纸屑源于[[意大利|意大利]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/confetti |title=Confetti - Definition and More from the Free Merriam-Webster Dictionary |publisher=Merriam-webster.com |date=2012-08-31 |accessdate=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517092319/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/confetti }}</ref>。现代意义上的彩色纸屑可以追溯到[[中世纪|中世纪]]后期，当时“[[异教徒|异教徒]]”的发展十分兴盛，他们在以谷类和甜食为主的特殊的象征性仪式上大量用到这些彩色纸屑。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/confetti |title=confetti - definition of confetti by The Free Dictionary |publisher=Thefreedictionary.com |date= |accessdate=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2022-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220614192010/https://www.thefreedictionary.com/confetti }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.candyfavorites.com/shop/catalog-jordan-almond-history.php |title=A Brief History of Jordan Almonds (Confetti) |publisher=Candy Favorites |date= |accessdate=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2022-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308183904/https://www.candyfavorites.com/shop/catalog-jordan-almond-history.php }}</ref>

